<div class="text-center">
  <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl">Find a Coach</h1>

  <p class="py-4">
    Coach's Companion • Effortlessly Manage Your Clients and Coaching Sessions with
    <a href="https://coachingfederation.org/experience-requirements", class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-sky-500/80">ICF Export Support</a>.
  </p>

  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 py-4">Currently in beta testing phase - <b>free access available for early users</b></p>

  <% if not user_signed_in? %>
    <p class="pt-4 pb-6 text-center sm:hidden">
      <%= link_to "Join for free", new_user_registration_path, class: "flex-shrink-0 rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600" %>
      <span class="mx-1">or</span> <%= link_to "Log in", new_user_session_path, class: "flex-shrink-0 rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600" %>
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl">Current usage</h2>
  Registered coaches: <%= @users.count %><br/>
  <%#
  <% @users.each do |user|
    <%= user.email , total clientspočet klientov: DOPLNIT<br/>
  <% end %>
  Total coached hours: <%= @total_hours %><br/>
  <br/>
  Read <%= link_to "What's new", whatsnew_path, class: "underline underline-offset-2 decoration-sky-500/80" %>,
  check the <a href="https://github.com/users/valasek/projects/2/views/1?layout=board" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-sky-500/80">Roadmap</a>
  or <%= link_to "leave a feedback", "https://forms.gle/rMP5FwtpPDMgSn337", class: "underline underline-offset-2 decoration-sky-500/80" %>.

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-6 text-left">
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-300 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6">
    <!-- Header section -->
    <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z" />
      </svg>
      Your Security Is Our Priority
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 mb-4 rounded-lg">
      <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Your data belongs to you. Client lists are private and visible only to you, with full rights to export your data or delete your account at any time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid for feature cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <!-- Authentication Card -->
      <div class="flex gap-3 p-4 bg-white/50 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/80 transition-colors">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 1 0-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z" />
        </svg>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Enterprise-Grade Authentication</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Your login is secured using Devise and bcrypt hashing - the same encryption standards trusted by financial institutions. Each password is uniquely salted and hashed for maximum protection.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
              <li>Multi-iteration bcrypt password hashing</li>
              <li>Secure session management</li>
              <li>Automatic session timeout</li>
              <li>Protection against credential stuffing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Browser Security Card -->
      <div class="flex gap-3 p-4 bg-white/50 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/80 transition-colors">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5.25 14.25h13.5m-13.5 0a3 3 0 0 1-3-3m3 3a3 3 0 1 0 0 6h13.5a3 3 0 1 0 0-6m-16.5-3a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h13.5a3 3 0 0 1 3 3m-19.5 0a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 .9-2.7L5.737 5.1a3.375 3.375 0 0 1 2.7-1.35h7.126c1.062 0 2.062.5 2.7 1.35l2.587 3.45a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 .9 2.7m0 0a3 3 0 0 1-3 3m0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0-6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm-3 6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0-6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z" />
        </svg>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Browser-Level Protection</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Industry-standard security headers protect your data during transmission and defend against common web vulnerabilities.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
              <li>Strict Transport Security (HSTS) enforced</li>
              <li>Protection against clickjacking (X-Frame-Options)</li>
              <li>Content Security Policy implementation</li>
              <li>Controlled cross-origin policies</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Data Protection Card -->
      <div class="flex gap-3 p-4 bg-white/50 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/80 transition-colors md:col-span-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
        </svg>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Advanced Data Protection</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Your data is protected by multiple layers of security, from encrypted transmission to secure storage:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4">
              <li>HTTPS encryption for all traffic</li>
              <li>Rails' encrypted credentials system</li>
              <li>Permission-based access control</li>
              <li>Regular security audits</li>
              <li>Secure referrer policy</li>
              <li>XSS attack prevention</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom message -->
    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
      <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Built on Rails' secure foundation and OWASP guidelines, we maintain strong security measures with regular updates to protect your data against evolving threats.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
